Interface Adapter<AdapterViewType extends <any>>

    public interface Adapter<AdapterViewType extends <any>>

      • notifyDataSetChanged

        void notifyDataSetChanged()
        Notifies all attached observers about the underlying data of the adapter having changed. This causes the adapter's views to be refreshed.

      • isNotifiedOnChange

        Returns, whether the method notifyDataSetChanged():void is automatically called when the adapter's underlying data has been changed, or not.
        Returns:
        True, if the method notifyDataSetChanged():void is automatically called when the adapter's underlying data has been changed, false otherwise
